        <p class="mb-3 text-justify"><strong>12.3 Severability</strong>. If any provision of this Agreement is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="chap13" class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-5 pb-2.5 border-b border-border">
